Chrysocolla is named from the Greek chrysos - "gold" and kolla - "glue" in allusion to the name of the material used to solder gold. Cuprite is named from the Latin, cuprum, meaning copper.

description:
The Battle of Palmito Ranch, also known as the Battle of Palmito Hill, is generally recognized as the final battle of the American Civil War. It was fought May 12 and 13, 1865, on the banks of the Rio Grande east of Brownsville, Texas and a few miles from the seaport of Los Brazos de Santiago, more than a month after Robert E. Lee had surrendered to Ulysses S. Grant in the Eastern Theater. Though the Battle of Appomattox Court House is identified as the last major battle of the war, Palmito Ranch was the last engagement between organized forces of the Union Army and Confederate States Army involving casualties. 
 The Wartech "Battle of Palmito Ranch" Assisted Opening Knife features a black finish 3CR13 steel drop point blade. The blade deploys rapidly through it's assisted opening technology. The handle of the knife is constructed of abs material. The bolster features the image of the confederate battle flag, and the handle of the knife depicts a scene from the Battle of Palmito Ranch between confederate forces battling Texas soldiers. 
 Features: 
 
 8 1/2" Overall Length 
 3 3/4" Stainless Steel Blade 
 4 3/4" ABS Handle

description:
New 2018 Charger V 3 Kiteboarding Twinskin Foil Kite All-terrain 
 CHARGER SIZES 
 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 15 / 18 / 22m 
 To celebrate nearly 2 decades of ARC/Twinskin history, Peter Lynn Kiteboarding is proud to introduce the Charger V3. The only foilkite design on the market dedicated to offering accessible, no bridle no hassle performance to water, land and snow based kite boarders. 
 This latest Arc stays true to its core identity; it is built for passionate kite flyers who enjoy the elegant flow that only a true old school kite can offer. 
 With the first Twinskin/ARC kites hitting the water before the turn of the century, Peter Lynn was amongst the earliest pioneers of the sport. With renowned names such as the S-ARC, Phantom, Bomba, Vortex and Venom the Peter Lynn Twinskin designs have remained innovative since the early days of kiteboarding. 
 By consistently standing out and staying true to our belief that simplicity works best, the latest kite once again offers all the benefits of the design. No pump, 4-lines, a small package, easy to set-up and pack down. Hit the beach, roll out your kite and start your session without having to leave anything behind. 
 The success of the Twinskin design is determined by the smooth way it delivers powerful performance. Whether you love to pull big kiteloops or simply enjoy a freeride session with high boosting jumps and floaty landings, the Charger delivers. 
 The Chargers C-shape is beautifully balanced because there are no heavy parts, this is reflected in the kites superior stability in all conditions and of course the famous auto zenith. The flexibility of the wing absorbs gusts allowing you to have a comfortable ride even in uncomfortable conditions. The high-end performance is phenomenal, the Charger never gives you an unsafe feeling and keeps its outstanding performing. Its windrange is unequalled in its kind. For the third generation Charger we have used a new fabric which is lighter and smoother, this results in a significant reduction of overall weight and better low end performance. 
 Born out of the love for kite flying in its purest form, Twinskin kites are designed to provide excellent performance in all disciplines: Kiteboarding, landboarding and snowkiting. This makes the Charger the ultimate all-round, all discipline and all conditions weapon for riders who wont limit themselves to style or terrain. 
 Never change a winning formula: this new version of the Charger embodies all the best aspects of the series. High wind stability, gust absorption, powerful boosts, smooth landings, proper bar pressure and superior longevity. 
 The Charger is designed to work in most conditions, its unbeaten stability makes it highly reliable and its shape and flexibility provide comfort even in unsteady winds. 
 ARC/Twinskin technology, the art of flying since 1999. 
 
 CHARACTERISTICS 
 Responsive and easy control 
 Feel where your kite is at all times 
 The Charger turns surprisingly quick and flies smoothly, challenging you to 
 do kite-loops and go big. 
 It can be flown with slack or tight rear lines. Its flying and turningspeed are not 
 affected by the rear line tension, which makes it suitable for various riding styles. 
 Every session a good session 
 Kiting made easy 
 No need to pump with the dual inflation zippers and no tangling lines with the 
 Velcro launch assistant tags. Every session you make with the Charger will be a 
 good session as you can focus on your kiting!
original_title: New 2018 Charger V 3 Kiteboarding Twinskin Foil Kite All-terrain

description:
Heat Safe Synthetic Straight Texture Lace Front in Rooted Dark Blonde *** Synthetic Lace Front wigs are a perfect way to achieve the natural look of a lace wig on a budget. Royal Crown Wigs Synthetic lace front wigs feature fine Heat Safe Fibers that looks and feels like human hair, matte finish without the fake synthetic shine and soft French lace hairline. Our stretch cap is designed for a snug fit and comfort allowing to wear the units with or without adhesive.

These heat safe wigs can be restyled using hot tools or fabric steamers. Great for reinventing yourself or recreating someone else. Great for Cosplay Characters, Parties, or just enjoying wigs. Synthetic Wigs help you be Daring and Different. 

Synthetic lace wigs have come a long way in recent years, thanks to technological advancements. It can be difficult to tell the difference between human hair and synthetic lace wigs. The biggest advantage with synthetic is that it can be worn right out of the box, without the need for professional styling. The fiber that is used has memory for curl, wave and volume. This means hair bounces back with minimal effort. It even holds up in the rain and snow, without frizzing or drooping.
There is no need for everyday styling so the overall care of synthetic lace wigs makes it very easy to maintain. You dont have to buy expensive products to keep the wig in good condition. It actually requires very little maintenance, when compared to human hair wigs.
These are also a much more cost-effective option. Because they look like human hair wigs, it may be a better choice for those on a budget.
With proper care and maintenance, you can expect your synthetic wig to last from 4-6 months.
original_title: Synthetic Straight Texture Lace Front in Rooted Dark Blonde

  HOW TO MEASURE FOR TOP 
 
 
  Your Band 
 
 
 
	Wearing a non-padded, non-minimizing everyday bra, measure just above the 
	bust by bringing a soft measuring tape across your back at band level, under 
	each arm (elbows down), then around the front to snugly but comfortably line 
	up with where your bra straps meet your cups. 
 
	TIP: Odd number or on the half inch? Round down to the nearest even number. 
 
	TIP: Did you measure yourself below the bust instead? Follow our guidelines 
	for above-the-bust measuring before entering your Band Size into the Perfect 
	Fit Calculator. 
 
 
 
  Your Bust 
 
 
 
	Measure across the fullest part of the bust by threading a soft measuring 
	tape across your back at band level and under each arm, being careful that 
	your elbows are down and that the tape isn't pulled away from the body in 
	the front. With the tape in position, take a breath in and out, allowing it 
	to slide to its most comfortable, non-binding fit. 
 
	TIP: If the measurement falls on the half inch, round up. 
 
 
 
  HOW TO MEASURE FOR BOTTOM 
 
 
  Waist Measurement 
 
 
 
  	Bend to one side to find natural indentation in torso. This is your natural 
	waist. Run tape around natural waistline, keeping tape parallel with floor 
	and one finger between body and tape for a more comfortable fit. 
 
 
 
  Hip Measurement 
 
 
 
  	Stand on a level surface with feet together. Measure around fullest part of 
	hips and bottom (approximately 7"-9" below waistline), keeping tape parallel 
	with floor.

description:
Loose Wave #2 Human Hair Wefts are 100g (3.5oz) bundles available from 3 origins In Natural Color. 
 Indian Hair 
 Indian hair is a quality hair and is highly regarded in the beauty industry. The hair is very light, airy, full but finer strands than others and easy to style. Indian hair usually comes in a natural straight and natural wave style. A popular wash and go hair because of the natural wave and faster drying time due to finer strands. 
 Peruvian Hair 
 Peruvian hair has become extremely popular. This hair is extremely durable and versatile and for this reason, allows you to style and curl it repeatedly with great results. This makes Peruvian hair a great multi-purpose hair as you can constantly change your look and style without damaging the hair too much. The hair is extremely soft and slightly silkier than Brazilian hair. As Peruvian hair is still relatively rare it is also usually relatively more expensive than other hair types. 
 Brazilian Hair 
 Brazilian hair is the MOST POPULAR hair type. The hair is typically soft, relatively thick and very durable. For this reason, the hair is suited to any style so it is always a great option whether you prefer a straight, wavy or curly style. Brazilian hair also handles color extremely well so if you buy Virgin Brazilian hair you can color the hair to any color you like. Due to the natural density, the hair has it is also less likely to frizz which is a big plus and you can also use fewer bundles to still maintain a full look.   *** Hands down, human hair looks and feels the most natural becausewellit is natural hair. There is nothing exactly like the feel, weight, and movement of a good quality human hair wig. (however, quality being the operative word is important to factor in as poor quality human hair is not worth the money in the long run at all!)Remy Human Hairis considered a premium option because it is generally easier to style and tangles much less due to all the follicles being kept in the same direction during construction.Human hair isremarkably soft with a shine and movement not easily duplicated by synthetic hair. Its versatility allows you to style it like your own hair with curls or bone straight withadurability that can last over a year!
original_title: Loose Wave #2 Human Hair Weft

 Ce collier a,au cours des sicles, fait  chavirer le cur  des femmes romantiques lorsque celles-ci se le faisaient offrir par leur amant.

 Ce bijous'adresse aux femmes qui ont  travers les torrents tumultueux  des premiers mois et qui refusent de s'agglutiner dans la vase marcageuse qu'est l' ennui de la routine . 
  destination de notre audience masculine, c e bijou est un prsent de choix  offrir  votre dulcine, qui vous sautera au cou pour vous remercier de lui montrer une si belle  attention . 
  
 Les dtails dela monture sont confectionns avec un  soin impeccable , et la couleur de la turquoise est clatante aux reflets du soleil. 
 Profitez tout de suite d'un des  coups de cur  de notre boutique ! 
 
 Correspondances astrologiques de la turquoise 
 La turquoise est lie aux signes astrologiques de la Balance, des Gmeaux, des Poissons, du Sagittaire, du Verseau, mais surtout du  Scorpion .  
 Ce signe, souvent considr comme  entrav par une trs forte intensit dnergie , parfois  tourn ngativement contre lui-mme , peut tre grandement aid par la turquoise qui  dnoue ses blocages , lui apporte  calme et paix intrieure .  
 Enfin, la turquoise est la  pierre de naissance  des enfants de dcembre et correspond au 18me anniversaire de mariage. 
 
 Vertus et bienfaits de la turquoise 
 LesApaches utilisaient dj la turquoise pour ses  vertus curatives : elle soignait les  piqres de scorpion et les  morsures de serpent . Une fois transforme en baume et applique sur les paupires, elle tait cense  viter la ccit . 
 Les bouddhistes tibtains lassociaient  du  corail rouge , lensemble symbolisant la  richesse spirituelle  et la  bonne fortune. 
 En lithothrapie, de nombreux bienfaits lui sont confres : elle protgerait son propritaire des  ondes ngatives  ou des  rayonnements nocifs , comme les ondes lectromagntiques. Sa capacit  absorber ces manations ngatives provoquerait un changement de couleur, voire une perte de brillance.  
 Sa couleur de ciel sans nuages lui a inspir d'tre  source dquilibre et dunification  : harmonie de lesprit et du corps, des tendances masculines et fminines...  
 Elle dveloppe la  finesse de lintuition  et de l empathie . Pour les personnes pratiquant la mditation, la turquoise se rvle un  catalyseur incontournable , en liaison avec le chakra du troisime il.  
 En relation avec le chakra de la gorge, elle  facilite la communication  et donc les  relations interpersonnelles : elleest exaltepar les orateursqui voient leur stress de parler en public diminuer et leur locution facilite.  
 Enfin, en harmonie avec le chakra du cur, elle apporte  calme et srnit , amplifiant les  capacits damour . 
 
 Histoires et lgendes autour de la turquoise 
 La turquoise tient son nom d'une  confusion  : les Vnitiens la rapportrent aux Europens, qui crurent qu'elle venait de  Turquie , alors qu'elle provenait de Perse, l o sjournent les plus beaux spcimens. Elle y tait employe comme  talisman contre le mauvais il , pour  orner les turbans  ou pour les sceaux des bagues que portaient les dignitaires. 
 En Amrique du Sud, la turquoise tait la  pierre des Dieux , indigne des hommes. Les Aztquesconfectionnaientde merveilleuses mosaques avec cette pierre jusqu' l'arrive des espagnols. 
 Les Indiens dAmrique du Nord y voyaient des  morceaux de ciel  De nos jours, les Navajos continuent  fabriquer de splendides bijoux de turquoise et dargent.

 La turquoise est un phosphate daluminium et de cuivre. Son systme cristallin est triclinique. Sa cassure est ingale, son clivage (tendance du cristal  se rompre) est nul. Cest un minral opaque  clat gras.

 1.How to comb the wig? 
 When you need to comb a wig, be gentle. Do not use regular brushes, and if you can, only comb it. It doesn\'t need combed every day, so let it rest. 
 2.How to keep shape? 
 While you\'re sitting at home, take it off and put it on a wig stand. The stand will help keep its shape and taking it off your head takes away from your own tugging and pulling hairs out. 
 3.How to wash the wig? 
 After washing a wig, do not shake it in a towel. Be careful and dry it piece-by-piece. This makes sure that strands of fibers don\'t fall off. Also, never style your wig while it\'s wet. Even those wet-to-style hair stylers are known to damage your wig. 
 4.How to dry the wig? 
 After saturating your wig in water, squeeze it dry. Don\'t wring it or the base of your wig could become mis-shaped and dry funny. 
 5.How to choose the conditioner? 
 While washing your hair, never use shampoo meant for natural hair. \'\'Even though normal conditioner is OK, the shampoo is too harsh and can lead to hair falling out. 
 6.How often do care the wig? 
 You can condition your hair every couple weeks or so, to keep it shiny and soft. Make sure you don\'t do that every day and be sure to rinse it all out or it could lead to build-up in your wig.Only wash your wig after wearing it for 25 times. The personal space cooler is compact, eco-friendly personal air cooler that pulls warm air from the room and cools and humidifies it. 
 
 The personal space cooler is freon free and doesnt need any toxic coolants. is freon free and doesnt need any toxic coolants. 
 
 
 Its not just safe to use but eco-friendly.  Other ac systems use a lot of power to try and cool an entire house or apartment, which is very costly! This personal air cooler actually cools the air around you, where you need it most while using the size and the power consumption of a small fan! Feel the arctic breeze with the alien air cooler.

9 Piece Clip-In Human Hair Wefts are 100g Sets that include 17 clips total.  
 
 Brazilian Hair 
 Brazilian hair is the MOST POPULAR hair type. The hair is typically soft, relatively thick and very durable. For this reason, the hair is suited to any style so it is always a great option whether you prefer a straight, wavy or curly style. Brazilian hair also handles color extremely well so if you buy Virgin Brazilian hair you can color the hair to any color you like. Due to the natural density, the hair has it is also less likely to frizz which is a big plus and you can also use fewer bundles to still maintain a full look.   *** Hands down, human hair looks and feels the most natural becausewellit is natural hair. There is nothing exactly like the feel, weight, and movement of a good quality human hair wig. (however, quality being the operative word is important to factor in as poor quality human hair is not worth the money in the long run at all!)Remy Human Hairis considered a premium option because it is generally easier to style and tangles much less due to all the follicles being kept in the same direction during construction.Human hair isremarkably soft with a shine and movement not easily duplicated by synthetic hair.  3. Once the speaker has been detected, select the product name ZF-510 to connect.

 FAQ and Solutions 
  1. Why cant the speaker connect to my device? 
 a. Check to ensure your devices BT function is enabled. 
 b. Make sure your device is within 3ft/1m of the speaker. 
 c. Delete the pairing record(s) on the speaker or your device. 
  2. Can I use the speaker to play music while charging? 
 To protect the long-term performance of the battery, it is better to charge it when  the speaker is turned off, especially when the battery is low. 
  3. Can I make or answer phone calls through the speaker? 
 No. The speaker does not feature a built-in microphone.

The majority of age-dependent changes that occur in our skin happen in the dermis, which can lose its thickness during the aging process. This is the result of changes in the fibroblasts, the cells responsible for collagen. description:
With a zippered, removable, padded camera cell for your camera equipment, the black  Ikigai Medium Rival Backpack offers added strength from within for protecting your gear from weather and impact. Inside the cell are padded, touch-fastening dividers for organizing a DSLR and up to seven lenses and related accessories. There's also an interior laptop sleeve and a zippered rear compartment on the backpack for an iPad/tablet. For doing more, the cell may be removed to convert the Rival Backpack into an overnight or day pack. By folding the lid underneath and in the back of the cell, one may then access gear through the pack's front zipper. A versatile pack, it has a zippered pocket on the top and left side as well as a stretch, mesh pocket on the right side for your water bottle. The bright green, interior lining makes it easier to locate items in low light. For style, the pack features matching zipper pulls and accents. 
 Carry your Rival Backpack with the padded top handle, or wear with the shoulder harness and waist belt. For comfort, the shoulder harness is padded, adjustable, ergonomically shaped, and has a chest connector for added stability. Both the chest connector and waist belt have quick-release buckles. The waist belt is also padded to make those long journeys not seem quite so long. Photographers will appreciate the sculpted back panels, which are made of padded mesh for cushioning, have channels for improved airflow, and a special lumbar panel. Made of triple-density, honeycomb rip stop nylon, your Rival Backpack is both strong and durable. In the event of inclement weather, simply deploy the included rain cover. When shooting on wet ground, the rain cover may be used as a ground cloth to help protect your knees and gear. 
 
 
 
 
 Removable camera cell which is essentially a zippered case with a handle. Photographers use this case for storing and organizing gear. With the cell removed the pack transitions to a day pack. 
 
 
 Removable rain cover that also function as a ground cloth. 
 
 
 The pack features top access for storing frequently used items. To enlarge the main compartment, simply remove the upper divider. 
 
 
 Color-coded, ergonomic zipper pullers allow for easy operation. This is especially helpful when wearing gloves. 
 
 
 Sculpted back panel with molded, vented contact points to improve airflow and help wick-away moisture. The panel is complemented by a curved harness system with an anatomic shape. 
 
 
 Stretch mesh side pockets for storing a water bottle and other accessories. 
 
 
 Rolling luggage trolley handle strap.

Its 110 wide detection angle and 3 pictures shot each time guarantee you'll never miss any unforgettable moments. This camera is not just widely used for outdoor scouting games and wildlife observation, but also popular in home and office security. Features: Superior Image and Video Captures: The trail and game camera captures 12 megapixel crisp, brightly colored photos in daytime (black and white at night) and 1080P video with sound. Super Fast Trigger Speed: With 120 super wide lens angle, 110 PIR detection angle and 1.0 second impressive fast trigger speed, you are guaranteed to never miss any of breathtaking moments by multi-shot feature which can take up to 3 photos and 10s video each trigger. Each detected movement is captured quickly and documented in real time. Long Night Vision Range: Built-in 26pcs 940nm infrared black LEDs provide up to 49 feet night time vision, which makes this camera a stealthy unit that does not intrude into the natural habitat, widely used in hunting, wildlife observation, home security, surveillance and scouting game. Long Battery Life and Durable: This camera runs on 4pcs AA batteries (not included), which can reach up to 12 months long battery life. It is well built to withstand extreme temperatures between -10 to 70, IP56 waterproof and can be left outdoors for long periods. description:
Premium Matcha Green Tea 
 Matcha is 100% green tea leaves,ground to a fine powder.Our Matcha is 100% natural and made to Japanese specifications. 
 30g matcha tin provides 30 servings. 
 Unlock the health benefits of Matcha 
 2 cups of brewed matcha contains7x the antioxidants of orange juice, 20x that of apple juice, and nearly 20g of calcium. 
 Taste the difference in every cup 
 A jammy-like smoothness with a very satisfying full cup. Luxury grade Japanese style green tea and Gyokuro gives a light astringent finish. 
 Grown with love 
 Producing this amazing tea is painstaking work. It is made using pure luxury tencha green tea and Gyokuro leaves that have been shaded under special shade covers for 3 weeks before plucking. Shading forces the tea plants into "overdrive" and produce higher than normal chlorophyll levels (the bright green stuff that contains all the nutrients). 
 Once plucked, the leaves are steamed and dried. Next, they are stripped of all stems and veins, resulting in a pure leaf that is stone-ground into the fine powderso when you drink it you ingest all of the leaf and all of it's nutrients. 
 This makes it very, very healthy. Matcha also provides a slow release of energy for up to six hours which helps keep you alert and focused. Brew a cup today - to your health!

description:
Vintage Old Crow Brass Store Display Bar Whiskey Statue 
 This item came from a Family bar business here in Las Vegas that had 7 locations and had been around since the 60's. When we liquidated the business we found countless old bar treasures that had been stored in the basement of one of the buildings. This is one of them. I Believe this is something different from what you might find on Ebay or On-line. While researching this item I found many "Award" variations that appear to be modern and look more like bowling trophy's than vintage liquor advertising. 
 This guy weighs in at almost 4lbs and is mounted using flat head screws that can be seen through the small tear on the bottom piece of felt. He's beautiful and has un-touched patina from the last 50+ years. His Pedastal has many small nics / scrapes / scuffs etc as seen in the pictures. The Brass has darkened over the ages. The brass "Old Crow" tag has lifted from the base as if the base has shrunk over the years, but is still firmy attached. 
 If your looking for "one of a kind" items, realistically this may be one of them. I was able to find One of them on an unrelated post from years ago after spending an hour trying to find an identical piece. 
 Approximate Dimensions: 11 1/2"T x 6 1/2"W x 4 1/2"W
original_title: Vintage Old Crow Brass Store Display Bar Whiskey Statue

description:
TheRichmond watch has a polished stainless steelcase. It has a whitedial with silver hands and indices. A butter-softdark brown calf's leatherstrap completes the look.  
 The Mark 1 is a unisex collection that suits both men and women alike. This model epitomises classic minimalism with clean lines and a modern aesthetic. description:
This string of 20 moon shaped lights are perfect for indoor and outdoor use. Since they are solar powered, you can place them near a window to recharge during the day or place them outside to have the lights automatically light up as soon as it's dark. 
  
 
 The solar light string consists of a solar cell, a rechargeable battery and LED lights. 
 During the day, light from the sun charges up the batteries. At night, the energy stored in the batteries is used to power the light. 
 The string is approximately 15.7 feet long. 
 It has two function modes: flashing or steady light. 
 The lights are weatherproof and can withstand rainy weather, but they are not waterproof (don't place them in the water!). 
 Charging time is 6-8 hours. 
 Steady ON mode can last 8-15 hours. 
 To install outdoors,find a place with clear and full exposure to the sun and insert the stake with the solar panel into the ground. 
 To install indoors, make sure the solar panel is arranged in a spot where it will receiveclear and full exposure to the sun. 
 Choose Pure White for a bright white glow; choose Warm White for a softer, yellowish glow. 
 Allow 12-20 days for delivery.

 Details: 
 Save up and cool down Sleeping in the heat is no easy feat. Either you're tossing and turning throughout the night or you're racking up a hefty electricity bill with the air conditioning on high all night. With the Gel'O Cool Mat, a good night's rest will no longer be at such a great expense of our planet or your bank account. 
 How it works  Staying comfortable in bed isn't about lying on an icy cold mat, but staying cool. The Gel'O Cool Pillow Mat disperses heat away from your head, keeping you at a comfortable temperature. Wider than many other pillow-sized cool mats on the market, and with more gel for support, your head can stay cool regardless of how you move during your sleep. 
 Use as an ice or heat pack: Gel'O Cool Mat can be placed in the refrigerator or freezer for use as an ice pack or microwaved for an instant heat pack that lasts around 10-30 minutes, depending on ambient temperature. The mat will stay soft and supple down to 14 deg. F/-10 deg. C so that it can easily conform to any part of the body that needs requirement. 
 Please note:  - User experiences will vary depending on mat position, temperature preference, ambient temperature, etc.   - Covering too much of the surface area may affect heat dissipation   - Use with caution and adult supervision for young children. Make sure the mat is removed on cooler days to prevent problems that may arise from over-cooling.  - This mat is designed for lying on. Sitting on the Gel'O Cool Mat will cause the gel inside to permanently shift, especially when used on a hard surface.
